### Get all tasks
GET https://localhost:7000/api/tasks

### Get task by ID
GET https://localhost:7000/api/tasks/1

### Create a new task
POST https://localhost:7000/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Sample Task"
}

### Update a task
PUT https://localhost:7000/api/tasks/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Task Title"
}

### Delete a task
DELETE https://localhost:7000/api/tasks/1
